%22%3EIs%20an%20ARM%20better%20than%20a%20fixed-rate%20mortgage%20in%202025%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EARMs%20tend%20to%20be%20popular%20with%20borrowers%20who%20don't%20plan%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20homes%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20If%20you%20sell%20your%20house%20before%20the%20initial%20fixed-rate%20period%20is%20over%2C%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20changing%20mortgage%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20plan%20to%20stay%20in%20your%20home%20for%20longer%2C%20Beeston%20recommends%20going%20with%20a%20classic%2030-year%20fixed-rate%20mortgage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%2030-year%20fixed%20is%20fantastic%20for%20risk-averse%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BNot%20all%20countries%20have%2030-year%20fixed%20loans.%20We%20are%20very%20lucky%20in%20America%20to%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20lock%20the%20rate%20of%20our%20loan%20for%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8184c9f-1a27-471f-8060-2503ddcbd2cc%5C%22%3EHow%20much%20can%20an%20ARM%20save%20you%20right%20now%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20you%20could%20save%20by%20opting%20for%20an%20ARM%20depends%20on%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emortgage%20lender%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20your%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESay%20you%20get%20quotes%20from%20a%20lender%20that%20show%20you%20can%20get%20a%205%2F1%20ARM%20with%20a%206.20%25%20interest%20rate%20or%20a%2030-year%20fixed-rate%20mortgage%20with%20a%206.80%25%20interest%20rate%20on%20a%20%24300%2C000%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20five%20years%2C%20the%20monthly%20payment%20on%20the%20ARM%20(not%20including%20taxes%20and%20insurance)%20would%20be%20%241%2C837%2C%20while%20the%20monthly%20payment%20on%20the%20fixed-rate%20mortgage%20would%20be%20%241%2C955.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20just%20an%20example.%20ARM%20rates%20can%20vary%20a%20lot%2C%20so%20if%20you'r