the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyielddesign.co%2Fproducts%2F850-ml-ceramic-french-press%3F_pos%3D2%26_sid%3D7a1b8a5d4%26_ss%3Dr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYield%20Ceramic%20French%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20modern%20design%20is%20a%20stylish%20take%20on%20the%20classic%20French%20press%20with%20four%20color%20options%20and%20a%20cylindrical%20copper%20pull.%20This%20thick-walled%20ceramic%20press%20makes%20a%20bold%20yet%20smooth%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%20but%20the%20handle%20is%20a%20bit%20narrow%20and%20the%20lid%20knocks%20around%20a%20bit%20when%20you%20pour.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Andrea%20Wawrzyn%2C%20freelance%20kitchen%20writer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20travel%3A%20Espro%20P1%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Espro%20P1%20French%20press%20on%20a%20wooden%20bar%20top.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fce9e2beadd8400183dfa22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20think%20the%20extra%20investment%20of%20the%20P1%20is%20worth%20saving%20yourself%20any%20number%20of%20inevitable%20agonies%20while%20using%20lesser%20travel%20French%20press.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELittle%20to%20no%20sediment%2C%20streamlined%2C%20leakproof%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECoffee%20gets%20bitter%20if%20you%20leave%20grounds%20in%20for%20too%20long%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20French%20presses%20are%20great%20for%20folks%20that%20roll%20out%20of%20bed%20and%20dash%20right%20out%20the%20door%2C%20and%20those%20who%20like%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20can%20produce%20a%20good%20cup%20of%20coffee%20just%20about%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20travel%20options%20and%20while%20they%20all%20work%20perfectly%20well%2C%20the%20Espro%20P1%20has%20a%20narrow%2C%20streamlined%20shape%20and%20a%20perfectly%20sealing%20filter%20and%20lid.%20Some%20sediment%20usually%20gets%20through%20most%20filters%2C%20but%20not%20the%20Espro's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECleaning%20the%20P1%20is%20every%20bit%20as%20easy%20as%20cleaning%20the%20P7.%20Because%20there%20are%20no%20coils%20holding%20a%20filter%20and%20plate%20in%20place%2C%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20scrub%20the%20filter%20itself%2C%20and%20unlike%20many%20of%20the%20other%20options%20we%20considered%2C%20it's%20dishwasher-safe%20(so%20long%20as%20it's%20placed%20on%20the%20top%20rack).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20shortcoming%20of%20this%2C%20and%20every%20travel%20French%20press%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20is%20that%20if%20you%20don't%20drink%20it%20quickly%20enough%2C%20your%20coffee%20is%20going%20to%20over-brew%2C%20and%20it%20will%20eventually%20get%20bitter.%C2%A0You%20can%20certainly%20find%20travel%20French%20presses%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20price%20of%20the%20P1%2C%20but%20they%20won't%20work%20as%20well%20and%20they're%20probably%20not%20going%20to%20be%20leakproof%2C%20which%20counts%20for%20a%20lot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20travel%20further%20afield%20than%20a%20commute%2C%20we%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-53940-20%26h%3D4ec411fd4010c91a658956cad76c07bd4c25877e6933e71ac5ef79853ac6d2c0%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f48e11%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-french-press%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FCOLETTI-Boulder-Camping-French-American%252Fdp%252FB09J9XJ41V%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColetti's%20Boulder%20Camping%20French%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20arguably%20the%20heaviest-duty%20French%20press%20we've%20tested.%20It%20has%20a%20large%2C%20welded-on%20handle%2C%20an%20ultra-tight%20silicone%20seal%20(which%20is%20great%20for%20keeping%20your%20coffee%20hot%20at%20camp)%2C%20and%20keeps%20grounds%20out%20of%20your%20cup%20with%20the%20best%20of%20them.%20We%20highly%20recommend%20it%20for%20people%20who%20are%20extra%20rough%20on%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20French%20press%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFilter%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20most%20important%20decision%20when%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20French%20press%20comes%20down%20to%20the%20filter%20on%20the%20plunger.%20The%20finer%20the%20filter%2C%20the%20fewer%20grounds%20you'll%20find%20in%20the%20bottom%20of%20your%20cup%2C%20and%20the%20less%20bitter%20your%20coffee%20will%20be%20(in%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-coffee-grinder%5C%22%3Ebest%20coffee%20grinder%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20help%20you%20out%2C%20too).%20Basic%20filters%20do%20the%20job%20for%20most%20people%2C%20but%20micro-%20and%20double-filters%20keep%20most%20of%20the%20fine%20particles%20out%20and%20the%20intended%20flavors%20unadulterated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Somewhat%20less%20important%20is%20the%20material%20of%20your%20French%20press.%20Plastic%20is%20light%2C%20cheap%2C%20and%20doesn't%20tend%20to%20shatter%20when%20it%20falls%20from%20the%20counter.%20Glass%20lasts%20longer%20and%20doesn't%20degrade%20over%20time%20in%20the%20way%20plastic%20does%2C%20but%20that's%20all%20provided%20that%20you%20don't%20drop%20it.%20Stainless%20steel%20French%20presses%20retain%20heat%20better%2C%20but%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20French%20presses%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20french%20presses%20sitting%20side%20by%20side%20on%20a%20kitchen%20counter%20with%20coffee%20grounds%20in%20front%20of%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fce9e5beadd8400183dfa23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20selecting%20French%20presses%20to%20test%2C%20we%20spoke%20to%20Sum%20Ngai%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoffeeprojectny.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoffee%20Project%20NY%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jordan%20Rosenaker%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-53940-20%26h%3Dff81f751ae493c5baaa3723e28e5587552b6b4b3788561282e288d226c716b7d%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f48e11%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-french-press%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.pjatr.com%252Ft%252FTUJGRk1NTEJGSEhLR01CRktORkdH%253Furl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fatlascoffeeclub.com%25252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAtlas%20Coffee%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Jim%20Munson%2C%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrooklynroasting.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrooklyn%20Roasting%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20what%20their%20favorite%20presses%20were%20and%20what%20the%20most%20critical%20components%20of%20a%20French%20press%20are.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20takeaway%3F%20How%20well%20a%20French%20press%20filters.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20choose%20a%20French%20press%2C%20it's%20all%20down%20to%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20clean%20and%20if%20the%20grinds%20will%20be%20properly%20filtered%20when%20I%20push%20down%20the%20filter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoffeeprojectny.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoffee%20Project%20NY%3C%2Fa%3E%20co-founder%20Sum%20Ngai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20checked%20to%20see%20if%20each%20French%20press's%20plunger%20worked%20smoothly%2C%20and%20noted%20whether%20or%20not%20there%20were%20gaps%20between%20the%20presses'%20filters%20and%20beakers.%20We%20also%20paid%20attention%20to%20the%20size%20and%20placement%20of%20the%20handle%20size%3B%20a%20poorly-designed%20handle%20could%20leave%20your%20knuckles%20grazing%20hot%20glass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbility%20to%20handle%20different%20sizes%20of%20coffee%20grounds%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20filled%20each%20press%20three%20times%20with%2054%20grams%20of%20coarse%20grinds%20and%20water%20at%20200%C2%B0%20Fahrenheit.%20We%20used%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-53940-20%26h%3Da7e8198cb4ac63f5959271ebab981c6725fdc9d864fb5958ec3de5c0c4e0536f%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f48e11%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-french-press%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.kruveinc.com%252Fproducts%252Fsifter-base%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Kruve%20sieve%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20measure%20the%20grinds%20to%20ensure%20accuracy%20and%20consistency%3A%201150%20micrometers%2C%201220%20micrometers%2C%20and%201280%20micrometers.%20We%20gave%20each%20pot%20a%20quick%20stir%20and%20let%20it%20steep%20for%20four%20to%20five%20minutes%20(four%20minutes%20for%20finer%20grounds%2C%20five%20minutes%20for%20coarser%20grounds)%20before%20evaluating%20the%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmount%20of%20sludge%20left%20behind%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20we%20kept%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20residual%20fine%20particulate%20and%20sludge%20after%20decanting%20each%20pot%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-53940-20%26h%3Da822726c8e6749defeaca2cdbaff522547bb869e6e3da5fdddb1bb0a216aa8a9%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f48e11%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-french-press%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.kruveinc.com%252Fproducts%252Fevoke-double-wall-serving-carafe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Kruve%20carafe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20amount%20found%20in%20each%20batch%20was%20almost%20identical%2C%20save%20for%20the%20finer%20(600-1000%20micrometer)%20grounds%2C%20which%20left%20more%20fine%20particulate%20matter%20in%20all%20but%20our%20stainless%20steel%20pick%2C%20the%20ESPRO%20P7.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEffort%20to%20clean%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20aggressively%20washed%20each%20strainer%2C%20although%20we%20found%20them%20all%20to%20be%20fairly%20sturdy.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20the%20P7's%20filter%20was%20the%20easiest%20to%20clean%20and%20coffee%20grounds%20didn't%20get%20stuck%20in%20its%20ultra-fine%20mesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrench%20press%20vs.%20pour-over%20coffee%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20between%20French%20press%20and%20pour-over%20coffee%20comes%20down%20to%20pressure%20and%20grind%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrewing%20French%20press%20coffee%20involves%20steeping%20coarsely%20ground%20beans%20(usually%20around%201%2C200%20micrometers)%20much%20like%20tea%2C%20and%20then%20pushing%20the%20solution%20through%20a%20filter%20to%20stop%20the%20brewing%20process.%20This%20pressure%20results%20in%20agitation%20and%20creates%20a%20bit%20of%20foam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPour-over%20coffee%20uses%20less%20coarse%20grounds%20(roughly%20900%20micrometers%2C%20but%20it%20really%20depends%20on%20your%20taste)%2C%20and%20while%20there%20is%20some%20steeping%20that%20occurs%20within%20the%20filter%2C%20the%20process%20employs%20gravity%20rather%20than%20applied%20pressure.%20It's%20a%20much%20more%20delicate%20brew%2C%20and%20a%20great%20way%20to%20drink%20finer%20and%20lighter-roast%20coffees%20(but%20again%2C%20it%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20taste).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20clean%20a%20French%20press%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Gator%20french%20press.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F624caad9bb219a00181bd721%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECoffee%20pots%20of%20all%20types%20are%20breeding%20grounds%20for%20mold%20spores%20and%20bacteria%2C%20so%20it's%20important%20to%20clean%20them%20regularly.%20However%2C%20French%20presses%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20consisting%20of%20a%20plate%2C%20a%20spiral%2C%20and%20a%20layer%20of%20mesh%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20tricky%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20coffee%20grounds%20get%20stuck%20inside%20them%20easily.%20Here's%20the%20cleaning%20method%20we%20find%20the%20most%20effective%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EFill%20the%20basin%20or%20carafe%20of%20your%20French%20press%20with%20hot%2C%20soapy%20water%20(regular%20dish%20soap%20works%20here).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPlunge%20the%20plunger%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20create%20a%20froth.%20This%20will%20generally%20get%20out%20most%20of%20the%20grounds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20go%20and%20pick%20out%20any%20stray%20grounds%2C%20but%20that%20might%20be%20a%20bit%20much%20for%20most%20people%2C%20and%20plunging%20the%20hot%20soapy%20water%20takes%20care%20of%20any%20mold%20or%20bacteria%20anyway.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-french-press%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745009962000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61dc84dd4ede320018b6dd32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-french-press%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20French%20press%20brews%20rich%20and%20smooth%20coffee.%20After%20testing%2017%20French%20press%20coffee%20makers%2C%20here%20are%20our%20top%20picks%20from%20Bodum%2C%20Fellow%2C%20and%20Espro.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22oburke%40businessinsider.com%20(Owen%20Burke)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-french-press%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2