at%20large%2C%20so%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20the%2083-inch%20S95F%20will%20use%20quantum%20dots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20less%20than%20half%20an%20inch%20thick%2C%20the%20S95F's%20profile%20is%20notably%20thinner%20than%20most%20competing%20QLED%20displays%2C%20which%20require%20thicker%20panels%20to%20accommodate%20their%20backlighting%20systems.%20All%20sizes%20also%20feature%20the%20brand's%20%26quot%3BOne%20Connect%20Box.%26quot%3B%20This%20separate%20component%20houses%20the%20TV's%20inputs%20rather%20than%20having%20them%20built%20into%20the%20panel.%20This%20approach%20gives%20users%20more%20flexibility%20with%20cable%20management%2C%20as%20you%20can%20either%20mount%20the%20box%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20TV%20or%20hide%20it%20out%20of%20view%20in%20a%20media%20console.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227787c246-9073-44fc-b366-92082b44426e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20S95F's%20bright%2C%20high-contrast%20picture%20is%20nearly%20flawless%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95F%20OLED%20TV%20resting%20on%20a%20media%20console%20with%20a%20soundbar%20in%20front.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68028204a466d2b74ab395d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV's%20OLED%20panel%20uses%20quantum%20dots%20to%20produce%20vivid%20colors.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20evaluate%20the%20S95F's%20picture%20performance%2C%20I%20put%20the%20TV%20through%20my%20typical%20testing%20process.%20This%20involves%20measuring%20brightness%20with%20a%20colorimeter%20and%20sampling%20various%20scenes%20I've%20curated%20from%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20that%20highlight%20different%20image%20quality%20attributes.%20For%20most%20of%20my%20testing%2C%20I%20used%20the%20TV's%20%26quot%3BFilmmaker%20Mode%26quot%3B%20since%20this%20preset%20offers%20the%20most%20accurate%20out-of-box%20picture%2C%20but%20I%20also%20sampled%20other%20modes%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20they%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20something%20seemed%20off%20about%20the%20S95F's%20picture.%20The%20colors%20were%20oddly%20dull%20in%20certain%20sequences%2C%20and%20the%20display's%20contrast%20looked%20flatter%20than%20expected.%20Another%20reviewer%20who%20attended%20the%20same%20session%20noticed%20similar%20issues.%20Samsung%20gave%20the%20TV%20a%20factory%20reset%2C%20and%20voila%2C%20those%20problems%20disappeared%2C%20and%20the%20S95F%20looked%20appropriately%20stunning.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20what%20the%20issue%20was%2C%20but%20the%20TV%20I%20tested%20was%20technically%20a%20pre-production%20unit%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20unusual%20for%20there%20to%20be%20some%20lingering%20software%20kinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20the%20S95F%20ultimately%20blew%20me%20away%20with%20its%20image%20quality.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20TVs%20I've%20tested%2C%20and%20it's%20second%20only%20to%20LG's%20brand-new%20G5%2C%20which%20gets%20a%20bit%20brighter.%20On%20a%2010%25%20test%20pattern%20(a%20white%20box%20that%20takes%20up%2010%25%20of%20the%20screen)%2C%20the%20TV%20put%20out%20an%20impressive%202%2C170%20nits%2C%20which%20is%20nearly%20500%20nits%20more%20than%20I%20measured%20on%20last%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-s95d-oled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES95D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20S95F%20was%20also%20able%20to%20sustain%20that%20brightness%20for%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20brightest%20elements%20of%20most%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20tend%20to%20be%20small%20highlights%2C%20a%2010%25%20test%20pattern%20is%20the%20most%20important%20for%20evaluating%20a%20display's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-dynamic-range%3C%2Fa%3E%20(HDR)%20impact.%20A%20lot%20of%20HDR%20content%20is%20mastered%20for%201%2C000%20nits%2C%20but%20titles%20produced%20for%202%2C000%20and%204%2C000%20nits%20are%20becoming%20more%20common.%20An%20OLED%20that%20can%20hit%20over%202%2C000%20nits%20is%20a%20major%20accomplishment%2C%20as%20it%20can%20offer%20a%20more%20accurate%20representation%20of%20how%20HDR%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20are%20supposed%20to%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95F%20TV%20displaying%20a%20video%20of%20a%20cityscape%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a3b0c6ad288d147e9ab3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S95F's%20infinite%20contrast%20ratio%20and%20high%20brightness%20enable%20incredible%20picture%20performance.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EScenes%20from%20%26quot%3BMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAquaman%26quot%3B%20on%204K%20Blu-ray%20were%20perfect%20showcases%20of%20the%20S95F's%20capabilities.%20Both%20are%20mastered%20for%20high%20brightness%20beyond%201%2C000%20nits%2C%20and%20the%20S95F%20was%20able%20to%20produce%20specular%20highlights%2C%20like%20lightning%20blasts%2C%20fiery%20explosions%2C%20and%20shimmering%20armor%2C%20with%20greater%20intensity%20than%20previous-generation%20OLEDs.%20And%20the%20TV's%20colors%20were%20also%20vibrant%2C%20bringing%20the%20vivid%20underwater%20world%20of%20Atlantis%20to%20life%20with%20rich%20saturation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20this%20is%20an%20OLED%2C%20the%20S95F's%20contrast%20performance%20is%20as%20good%20as%20it%20gets.%20The%20OLED%20panel's%20pixel-level%20dimming%20enables%20an%20infinite%20contrast%20ratio%20with%20deep%20black%20levels%20that%20completely%20disappear%20into%20a%20dark%20room.%20Scenes%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B1917%26quot%3B%20were%20perfect%20examples%20of%20this%3A%20shadows%20appeared%20inky%20while%20bright%20elements%20of%20the%20image%2C%20like%20a%20flashlight%20or%20exploding%20flare%2C%20popped%20against%20black%20backgrounds%20without%20any%20troublesome%20blooming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20top%20QLED%20TVs%20with%20high-end%20Mini%20LED%20panels%20are%20prone%20to%20some%20backlight%20fluctuations%20and%20halos%20during%20tricky%20sequences%2C%20like%20the%20burning%20church%20scene%20in%20%26quot%3B1917%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20S95F%20handled%20this%20type%20of%20content%20without%20any%20issues.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20OLED%20tech%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fqled-vs-oled%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQLED%20vs.%20OLED%20comparison%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20high-quality%204K%20content%2C%20I%20also%20sampled%20lower-resolution%20HD%20sources%20from%20YouTube%20and%20Samsung%20TV%20Plus%20(the%20brand's%20free%20ad-supported%20streaming%20app).%20Though%20Sony%20often%20gets%20heralded%20for%20its%20industry-leading%20upscaling%20and%20picture%20processing%2C%20Samsung%20and%20LG%20have%20made%20big%20strides%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20and%20the%20S95F%20is%20further%20proof%20of%20that.%20Sure%2C%20lower-quality%20material%20still%20looks%20noticeably%20softer%20and%20compressed%20than%20native%204K%20content%2C%20but%20the%20S95F's%20processing%20is%20a%20clear%20step%20above%20that%20of%20TVs%20from%20cheaper%20brands%20like%20TCL%2C%20Hisense%2C%20and%20Roku.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95F's%20gaming%20capabilities%20are%20on%20par%20with%20what%20shoppers%20should%20expect%20from%20a%20flagship%20set%20in%20this%20class.%20You%20get%20variable%20refresh%20rate%20(VRR)%20and%20auto%20low%20latency%20mode%20(ALLM)%20support%20to%20enable%20smooth%20gameplay%20and%20low%20input%20lag.%20But%20the%20S95F%20offers%20an%20even%20higher%20refresh%20rate%20than%20last%20year's%20S95D%2C%20jumping%20from%20144Hz%20to%20165Hz.%20This%20feature%20only%20benefits%20PC%20gamers%20with%20a%20high-end%20graphics%20card%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20an%20impressive%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20competition%2C%20only%20LG's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Flg-2025-c5-g5-oled-4k-tvs-price-release-specs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EG5%20OLED%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20go%20toe-to-toe%20with%20the%20S95F's%20picture%20capabilities.%20However%2C%20the%20G5%20can%20get%20even%20brighter%2C%20which%20gives%20highlights%20in%20certain%20HDR%20content%20a%20bit%20more%20intensity.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20S95F%20has%20an%20edge%20in%20color%20volume%2C%20giving%20especially%20bright%20colors%20more%20saturation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a636a5ec-c2d5-4d96-b8a5-f7cad1102b49%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Glare-free%20screen%5C%22%3EThe%20TV's%20glare-free%20tech%20is%20great%20for%20reducing%20reflections%2C%20but%20gives%20dark%20scenes%20a%20faded%20look%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222253%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20Samsung%20S95F%20TV%20displaying%20a%20black%20screen%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68029f3c3fe8d392836383ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221690%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S95F's%20matte%20screen%20nearly%20eliminates%20direct%20reflections%2C%20but%20it%20elevates%20black%20levels%20a%20bit%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20last%20year's%20S95D%2C%20the%20S95F%20uses%20Samsung's%20glare-free%20technology%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20a%20matte%20screen%20rather%20than%20a%20glossy%20one.%20Glossy%20screens%20are%20used%20on%20most%20competing%20TVs%2C%20like%20LG's%20G5%2C%20and%20though%20they're%20great%20for%20preserving%20high%20contrast%2C%20they%20can%20lead%20to%20mirror-like%20reflections%20when%20watching%20TV%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95F's%20matte%20screen%20can%20scatter%20and%20diffuse%20glare%20in%20a%20way%20that%20nearly%20eliminates%20direct%20reflections.%20Samsung%20says%20this%20second-generation%20glare-free%20screen%20offers%20even%20better%20performance%20than%20last%20year's%20version.%20I%20couldn't%20compare%20the%20S95D%20and%20S95F%20side-by-side%2C%20but%20the%20S95F%20certainly%20does%20an%20incredible%20job%20of%20reducing%20glare.%20With%20the%20lights%20on%2C%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20bothersome%20reflections%20on%20the%20screen.%20Sure%2C%20if%20you%20shine%20light%20directly%20on%20the%20panel%2C%20you%20will%20see%20some%20hazy%20glare%2C%20but%20this%20effect%20is%20nothing%20like%20the%20mirror%20quality%20of%20a%20glossy-style%20OLED.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20S95D%20in%20a%20dark%20room%20with%20diffuse%20glare%20on%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20screen%20caused%20by%20light%20being%20shone%20directly%20on%20the%20panel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68029faa3fe8d3928363840d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20glare%20is%20still%20visible%20when%20shining%20light%20directly%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20but%20it's%20much%20more%20diffuse%20than%20the%20mirror-like%20quality%20of%20a%20glossy%20screen.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20S95F's%20matte%20screen%20is%20still%20prone%20to%20the%20same%20key%20drawback%20I%20encountered%20with%20last%20year's%20S95D%3A%20it%20elevates%20black%20levels%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%20The%20way%20the%20anti-glare%20filter%20scatters%20light%20causes%20black%20levels%20to%20lose%20their%20inkiness%20and%20take%20on%20a%20slightly%20faded%20look.%20This%20is%20most%20evident%20when%20watching%20content%20with%20many%20dim%20scenes.%20In%20a%20dark%20room%2C%20however%2C%20the%20S95F's%20black%20levels%20are%20as%20deep%20as%20on%20competing%20OLED%20TVs%20with%20glossy%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20this%20effect%20was%20still%20evident%20on%20the%20S95F%2C%20it%20bothered%20me%20slightly%20less%20than%20it%20did%20on%20last%20year's%20S95D.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20the%20new%20screen%20handles%20contrast%20a%20bit%20better%20or%20if%20I've%20just%20become%20more%20accustomed%20to%20the%20look%20of%20matte%20panels%2C%20but%20I%20appreciated%20the%20overall%20benefits%20of%20the%20S95F's%20glare-free%20tech%20more%20than%20I%20did%20on%20the%20S95D.%20Ultimately%2C%20I%20still%20much%20prefer%20the%20deeper%20black%20levels%20you%20get%20with%20a%20glossy%20panel%2C%20but%20if%20your%20room%20is%20plagued%20by%20reflections%20that%20you%20can't%20(or%20don't%20want%20to)%20fix%20with%20curtains%2C%20the%20S95F%20is%20a%20great%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2466e71-ce13-4892-b118-25f5a00b0539%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20features%5C%22%3ESamsung's%20smart%20TV%20system%20is%20solid%2C%20but%20the%20new%20AI%20features%20are%20underwhelming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221950%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95F%20displaying%20the%20Tizen%20smart%20TV%20homepage%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a05e3fe8d3928363842c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamsung's%20Tizen%20interface%20is%20solid%20with%20easy-to-navigate%20sections%20for%20various%20apps%20and%20services.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95F%20uses%20the%20latest%20version%20of%20Samsung's%20Tizen%20smart%20TV%20operating%20system.%20This%20platform%20is%20decent%20overall%2C%20with%20solid%20navigation%20and%20all%20the%20major%20functions%20you%20could%20need.%20In%20general%20design%20and%20usability%2C%20I%20put%20it%20on%20par%20with%20LG's%20similar%20webOS%20system%20and%20a%20step%20above%20Amazon's%20Fire%20TV%20OS%2C%20which%20I%20find%20too%20cluttered%20and%20filled%20with%20sponsored%20content.%20However%2C%20I%20still%20prefer%20the%20Google%20TV%20and%20Roku%20OS%20systems%20thanks%20to%20their%20more%20streamlined%20interfaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95F's%20sidebar%20panel%20offers%20access%20to%20dedicated%20pages%20for%20search%2C%20ambient%20mode%2C%20Samsung%20Daily%2B%20(health%2C%20work%2C%20and%20smart%20device%20control%20apps)%2C%20and%20a%20gaming%20hub.%20The%20gaming%20hub%20is%20where%20you'll%20find%20cloud%20services%20like%20Nvidia%20GeForce%20Now%2C%20Amazon%20Luna%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fxbox-game-pass%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXbox%20Game%20Pass%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Samsung%20and%20LG%20(via%20a%20future%20update)%20are%20the%20only%20brands%20that%20support%20the%20Xbox%20app%2C%20which%20lets%20subscribers%20play%20Xbox%20games%20without%20a%20console.%20Performance%20heavily%20depends%20on%20your%20internet%20connection%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20cool%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20voice%20control%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20between%20Samsung's%20Bixby%20virtual%20assistant%20or%20Amazon%20Alexa.%20Spoken%20commands%20can%20be%20given%20hands-free%20with%20a%20wake%20word%20or%20via%20a%20button%20press%20on%20the%20included%20SolarCell%20remote.%20The%20remote%20is%20similar%20to%20past%20models%20with%20a%20compact%20design%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20charge%20via%20sunlight%20or%20indoor%20lights%2C%20so%20you%20never%20need%20to%20replace%20batteries%20(it%20can%20also%20be%20recharged%20much%20quicker%20via%20USB-C).%20However%2C%20it's%20disappointing%20that%20it%20isn't%20backlit%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20common%20feature%20on%20remotes%20from%20brands%20like%20Hisense%20and%20TCL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20brand's%20marketing%20materials%2C%20Samsung%20has%20been%20emphasizing%20its%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109091339m9-20%26h%3D6103f5bb759021d41f4dd2a8c589e5af7f2cf89390a4cb6552e38e3008f91fc2%26postID%3D680280f93d37c2e3ad4c4621%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-s95f-oled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.samsung.com%252Fus%252Ftvs%252Fvision-ai-tv%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVision%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20suite%20of%20smart%20features%20across%20its%202025%20TVs.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20these%20AI-powered%20functions%20are%20just%20upgraded%20versions%20of%20features%20that%20the%20company's%20older%20TV%20models%20already%20supported.%20Various%20AI%20upscaling%20and%20image%2Faudio%20enhancement%20modes%20have%20been%20improved%2C%20but%20are%20nothing%20new.%20These%20features%20can%20be%20useful%20for%20users%20unhappy%20with%20the%20TV's%20image%20or%20audio%20quality%2C%20but%20they%20often%20introduce%20unnecessary%20adjustments.%20Generally%2C%20I%20recommend%20avoiding%20these%20settings%20and%20just%20using%20Filmmaker%20or%20Standard%20mode.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20few%20AI%20features%20that%20are%20genuinely%20new%20for%202025%20are%20underwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20look%20at%20the%20Click%20to%20Search%20feature%20on%20a%20Samsung%202025%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a6223fe8d392836385e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221055%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamsung's%20AI-powered%20Click%20to%20Search%20offers%20information%20about%20the%20content%20you're%20watching.%20(The%20feature%20is%20pictured%20on%20a%20QN900F%20TV%20model%20but%20works%20the%20same%20on%20the%20S95F.)%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20there's%20a%20Live%20Translate%20function%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20offer%20real-time%20subtitles%20in%20one%20of%20seven%20languages.%20That%20sounds%20cool%2C%20but%20this%20feature%20only%20works%20with%20live%20broadcasts%20from%20an%20over-the-air%20(OTA)%20antenna.%20Many%20people%20watch%20TV%20via%20cable%20or%20streaming%2C%20so%20that's%20a%20notable%20limitation.%20Since%20I%20didn't%20have%20an%20antenna%20handy%20during%20my%20review%20session%2C%20I%20could%20not%20test%20this%20feature%2C%20but%20I'll%20try%20it%20when%20I%20review%20Samsung's%20other%20TV%20models%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%20That%20said%2C%20given%20this%20restriction%20to%20OTA%20broadcasts%2C%20I%20can't%20imagine%20this%20being%20a%20big%20selling%20point%20in%20its%20current%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung%20has%20also%20been%20touting%20a%20new%20Click%20to%20Search%20feature%20that%20lets%20you%20click%20a%20button%20on%20the%20remote%20to%20pull%20up%20info%20about%20the%20content%20you're%20viewing%2C%20including%20details%20about%20the%20cast%20on%20screen.%20This%20sounds%20similar%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109091339m9-20%26h%3D1832bf9e83420e76af092003e188dac3a6a44878f1f5f9c170bf672c30ff9aa2%26postID%3D680280f93d37c2e3ad4c4621%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-s95f-oled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fsalp%252Fxray%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX-Ray%3C%2Fa%3E%20feature%20that%20Amazon%20supports%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fwhat-is-prime-video%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Video%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20only%20works%20with%20live%20OTA%20broadcasts%2C%20cable%20TV%2C%20and%20Samsung%20TV%20Plus.%20So%2C%20it%20won't%20work%20when%20streaming%20popular%20apps%20like%20Netflix%20or%20Disney%20Plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20compatible%20sources%2C%20Click%20to%20Search%20is%20kind%20of%20lame.%20I%20tested%20this%20function%20while%20channel%20surfing%20through%20Samsung%20TV%20Plus%20and%20pulled%20it%20up%20while%20%26quot%3BLa%20La%20Land%26quot%3B%20was%20playing.%20A%20side%20panel%20displayed%20the%20name%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20its%20IMDB%20score%2C%20and%20a%20list%20of%20other%20titles%20coming%20up%20on%20the%20same%20channel.%20Another%20tab%20listed%20the%20main%20actors%20in%20the%20film%20and%20showed%20some%20other%20movies%20they're%20in.%20That's%20all%20fine%2C%20but%20pretty%20limited%20compared%20to%20what%20Prime%20Video's%20X-Ray%20can%20do.%20X-Ray%20will%20pull%20up%20all%20of%20the%20actors%20in%20the%20specific%20scene%20you're%20watching%2C%20not%20just%20the%20top-billed%20people%20in%20the%20movie%20as%20a%20whole.%20With%20its%20limited%20compatibility%20and%20info%2C%20I%20can't%20see%20many%20people%20using%20this%20function%20too%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20want%20to%20dive%20more%20deeply%20into%20Vision%20AI%20features%20when%20I%20review%20other%20Samsung%20TVs%20this%20year%2C%20but%20based%20on%20my%20initial%20time%20with%20these%20functions%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20a%20major%20evolution%20in%20the%20brand's%20smart%20TV%20capabilities%20compared%20to%20last%20year's%20models.%20But%20honestly%2C%20that's%20OK.%20Samsung's%20smart%20TVs%20have%20already%20been%20plenty%20smart%2C%20so%20the%20S95F's%20advancements%20are%20fine.%20But%20the%20idea%20that%20Samsung's%202025%20models%20are%20ushering%20in%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20%26quot%3BAI%20TVs%26quot%3B%20seems%20overblown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d3d7fc1-1e0c-4872-ac06-64c9b588c6d2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Samsung%20S95F%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221682%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Insider%20Reviews%20editor%20Steven%20Cohen%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch%20watching%20a%20Samsung%20S95F%20OLED%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A