sday%20afternoon%2C%20driving%20from%20Nebraska%20to%20Iowa%2C%20when%20the%20news%20came%3A%20His%20group%20of%20AmeriCorps%20members%20was%20being%20sent%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Thursday%2C%20Walker-Price's%20whole%20crew%20had%20to%20be%20on%20planes.%20They%20were%20only%20three%20months%20into%20a%20ten-month%20service%20contract%20and%20had%20been%20preparing%20to%20go%20to%20Minnesota%20to%20fix%20cabins%20and%20trails%20at%20a%20campground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happened%20so%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20Walker-Price%2C%2020%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20minute%20we%20were%20working%2C%20and%20the%20next%20minute%20we%20were%20told%20to%20pack%20our%20bags%20and%20come%20back%20to%20Iowa%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20get%20on%20the%20flight.%20It%20took%20everybody%20by%20surprise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Javon%20Walker-Pierce%20taking%20a%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a232c6ad288d147e9a3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJavon%20Walker-Pierce%20on%20the%20job%20for%20AmeriCorps.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Javon%20Walker-Pierce%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalker-Price%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20AmeriCorps%20volunteers%20who%20are%20dealing%20with%20%E2%80%94%20or%20bracing%20for%20%E2%80%94%20the%20firings%20that%20have%20decimated%20many%20other%20federal%20agencies.%20Members%20of%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20office%20visited%20both%20AmeriCorps%20and%20Peace%20Corps%20headquarters%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20throwing%20the%20agencies'%20futures%20into%20question.%20A%20representative%20for%20the%20Peace%20Corps%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20the%20agency%20is%20subject%20to%20the%20federal%20hiring%20freeze%2C%20%26quot%3Bvolunteer%20recruitment%20activities%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20no%20staff%20have%20been%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201993%20a