EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20nine%20early-career%20AmeriCorps%20and%20Peace%20Corps%20members%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20full-time%20agency%20or%20partner%20organization%20staff%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabout%20what%20the%20cuts%20mean%20for%20their%20futures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20that%20roughly%2075%25%20of%20full-time%20AmeriCorps%20employees%20were%20placed%20on%20administrative%20leave%20this%20week.%20The%20agency%20reportedly%20shut%20down%20a%20program%20that%20focuses%20in%20part%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnation%2F2025%2F04%2F16%2Famericorps-cuts-doge-trump%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisaster%20preparedness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sending%20home%20all%20members%20and%20placing%20them%20on%20administrative%20leave.%20There's%20no%20clear%20timeline%20for%20when%20employees%20could%20return%20to%20work%20or%20be%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20administration%20official%20said%20that%20the%20staff%20shake-up%20comes%20because%20%26quot%3BAmeriCorps%20failed%20eight%20consecutive%20audits%20and%20is%20entrusted%20with%20over%20%241%20billion%20in%20taxpayer%20dollars%20every%20year.%26quot%3B%20Representatives%20for%20AmeriCorps%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Peace%20Corps%20rep%20said%20the%20agency%20is%20in%20%26quot%3Bfull%20compliance%20with%20executive%20orders%20and%20other%20presidential%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221cdac5d-32c4-41ff-84d6-e4cbce620e3d%5C%22%3E'I%20don't%20know%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20do'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20most%20of%20the%20members%20BI%20spoke%20with%20had%20not%20been%20cut%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20all%20said%20they're%20bracing%20for%20the%20possibility%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20writing%20is%20on%20the%20wall%2C%26quot%3B%20a%2024-year-old%20Peace%20Corps%20member%20in%20the%20South%20Pacific%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20AmeriCorps%20community%20that%20I'm%20involved%20with%20is%20just%20anxious%20about%20if%20cuts%20do%20happen%2C%20how%20do%20we%20pay%20our%20bills%3F%26quot%3B%20a%2026-year-old%20AmeriCorps%20member%20working%20in%20Texas%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20keep%20moving%20forward%20with%20our%20lives%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20AmeriCorps%20seemed%20like%20a%20solid%20entryway%20to%20a%20stable%20career%20path%20%E2%80%94%20the%2026-year-old%20said%20they%20thought%20of%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstepping%20stone%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20permanent%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeredith%20B.%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20AmeriCorps%20member%20in%20Boston%2C%20said%20she%20took%20her%20job%2C%20in%20part%2C%20because%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-worried-unemployment-layoffs-recession-jobs-hiring-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshaky%20labor%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I'll%20work%20for%20the%20government%20in%20an%20almost%20unrelated%20position%20that%20still%20employs%20my%20skills.%20This%20will%20be%20safe.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20willing%20to%20hire%20people%20who%20don't%20have%20much%20experience%2C%20and%20they%20teach%20you%20all%20the%20skills%20you%20need%20in%20a%20very%20open%20environment%20where%20it's%20OK%20to%20make%20mistakes%20and%20not%20know%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20a%2022-year-old%20AmeriCorps%20member%20in%20North%20Carolina%20said.%20%26quot%3BBy%20the%20end%2C%20you%20have%20those%20skills%20to%20go%20into%20whatever%20other%20career%20you're%20trying%20to%20go%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20members%20are%20wondering%20whether%20their%20months%2C%20or%20in%20some%20cases%20years%2C%20of%20service%20will%20still%20set%20them%20up%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20knew%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Peace%20Corps%20member%20said%20about%20his%20contingency%20plan%20if%20his%20job%20gets%20cut.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20rough%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20off-ramps%20I%20would've%20had%20previously%20have%20now%20either%20been%20cut%20or%20have%20been%20severely%20negatively%20affected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wanted%20to%20work%20for%20the%20federal%20government%20or%20a%20nonprofit%20organization%20that%20received%20now-slashed%20federal%20funding.%20He's%20worried%20that%20the%20few%20government%20jobs%20that%20are%20available%20will%20go%20to%20older%20people%20with%20more%20experience%20and%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20being%20flooded%20by%20very%2C%20very%20well-qualified%20government%20workers%20that%20I%20cannot%20compete%20with.%20So%20right%20now%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeredith%20B.%20said%20that%20she%20doesn't%20have%20any%20sort%20of%20safety%20net%2C%20like%20many%20other%20people%20her%20age.%20All%20of%20her%20belongings%20were%20ruined%20in%20Hurricane%20Helene%20%E2%80%94%20what%20she%20has%20left%20fits%20in%20the%20two%20suitcases%20she%20brought%20with%20her%20to%20Boston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20all%20the%20things%20I%20own%20in%20this%20world%20now%2C%20except%20I%20bought%20a%20pair%20of%20pants%20recently%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268936eca-6105-49b6-a608-f21df82b48ca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20path%20forward%2C%20suddenly%20blocked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20worker%20at%20the%20agency%20who%20served%20under%20Obama%2C%20Trump%2C%20and%20Biden%20also%20said%20AmeriCorps%20set%20young%20people%20up%20for%20a%20career%20in%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20it%20time%20and%20time%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20service%20connected%20them%20to%20a%20lifetime%20of%20continued%20commitment%20and%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20future%20jobs%20that%20hang%20in%20the%20balance%20%E2%80%94%20many%20members%20of%20AmeriCorps%20and%20the%20Peace%20Corps%20use%20education%20grants%20from%20the%20programs%20to%20pay%20off%20student%20loans%20or%20get%20another%20degree.%20Libby%20Stegger%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20Civic%20Bridgers%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20which%20partners%20with%20AmeriCorps%2C%20said%20she%20doesn't%20know%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20members'%20education%20awards%20if%20funding%20is%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20something%20that%20is%20very%20appealing%20to%20folks%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20and%20especially%20to%20folks%20who%20are%20early%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20education%20grants.%20%26quot%3BParticularly%20for%20people%20who%20might%20otherwise%20not%20have%20access%20to%20those%20kinds%20of%20education%20funding%20opportunities%2C%20that%20is%20a%20tremendous%20benefit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2026-year-old%20AmeriCorps%20member%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bwouldn't%20even%20consider%26quot%3B%20grad%20school%20if%20his%20education%20award%20gets%20cut%2C%20and%20the%20Peace%20Corps%20member%20said%20going%20to%20grad%20school%20with%20the%20money%20had%20been%20key%20to%20his%20long-term%20goal%20of%20working%20in%20the%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuts%20are%20also%20rippling%20down%20to%20students%20who%20are%20still%20in%20high%20school%20or%20college.%20Elizabeth%20Baz%2C%2018%2C%20applied%20to%20AmeriCorps%20for%20a%20gap%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20really%20hoping%20that%20AmeriCorps%20would%20kind%20of%20help%20me%20just%20get%20my%20life%20together%20and%20help%20me%20gain%20some%20more%20self-discipline%20and%20more%20life%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Baz%20said%20she%20still%20plans%20to%20take%20a%20gap%20year%20but%20doesn't%20know%20yet%20what%20she'll%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AmeriCorps%20member%20in%20North%20Carolina%20said%20it's%20upsetting%20to%20think%20that%20younger%20people%20won't%20have%20the%20same%20opportunities%20she%20did.%20The%20AmeriCorps%20member%20in%20Texas%20said%20his%20service%20made%20him%20feel%20more%20American%2C%20and%20he%20worries%20his%20family%20won't%20have%20that%20same%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20here%20on%20my%20desk%20a%20picture%20of%20my%20little%20nephews%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20choking%20up.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20about%20all%20the%20work%20that%20we're%20doing%20now%20is%20to%20potentially%20have%20that%20same%20space%20for%20them%20to%20also%20experience%20whenever%20they're%20my%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Thursday%20night%2C%20Walker-Price%20had%20made%20it%20home%20to%20Virginia%2C%20but%20he%20had%20trouble%20sleeping%20in%20the%20quiet.%20He%20had%20gotten%20used%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20his%20AmeriCorps%20colleagues%2C%20who%20had%20become%20more%20like%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20planned%20on%20being%20with%20AmeriCorps%20for%2010%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Walker-Price%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20just%20being%20sent%20home%20immediately%2C%20now%20it's%20like%2C%20what%20am%20I%20going%20to%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aatecotzky%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eatecotzky%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejkaplan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aallisonkelly%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eallisonkelly%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%