1139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Pod%204%20hub%20on%20a%20carpeted%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68016bd8a466d2b74ab38490%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pod%204%20hub%20connects%20to%20WiFi%20and%20holds%20the%20water%20tank.%20One%20hub%20can%20power%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20bed.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20terminology%20around%20the%20Pod%204%20can%20be%20confusing%2C%20but%20at%20its%20foundational%20level%2C%20there%20are%20two%20parts%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cover%20and%20the%20hub.%20The%20cover%20slips%20over%20any%20mattress%20like%20a%20fitted%20sheet%20and%20connects%20to%20the%20hub%20via%20fabric-covered%20tubes.%20The%20hub%20is%20the%20brains%20of%20the%20operation%20and%20houses%20things%20like%20the%20water%20tank%20and%20is%20the%20point%20of%20connection%20for%20WiFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hub%20is%20the%20size%20of%20an%20old-school%20desktop%20computer%20and%2C%20minus%20a%20CD%20tray%20slot%2C%20kind%20of%20looks%20like%20one.%20The%20hub%20is%20covered%20in%20a%20dark%20texture%20fabric%20which%20helps%20it%20blend%20in%2C%20but%20its%20presence%20is%20notable.%20It%20needs%20to%20sit%20upright%20so%20it%20can't%20lay%20on%20its%20side%20underneath%20a%20bed%20frame.%20It%20also%20needs%20a%20spot%20to%20live%20within%207.75%20-%208.25%20feet%20of%20the%20mattress%20cover%20(depending%20on%20the%20size)%20that%20it's%20physically%20connected%20to.%20Unlike%20some%20other%20competing%20products%2C%20however%2C%20you%20only%20need%20one%20hub%20to%20heat%20and%20cool%20two%20sides%20of%20a%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20carved%20out%20a%20spot%20for%20the%20hub%20in%20my%20room%20between%20an%20accent%20chair%20and%20nightstand%20to%20hide%20it%20away.%20Although%20I%20would%20have%20preferred%20not%20to%20see%20the%20hub%20at%20all%2C%20it%20did%20disappear%20from%20my%20vision%20after%20a%20few%20days.%20Beyond%20its%20aesthetic%2C%20the%20hub%20needs%20proximity%20to%20a%20wireless%20internet%20connection%20so%20it%20won't%20necessarily%20sit%20in%20the%20most%20ideal%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pod%204%20cover%20should%20only%20be%20a%20very%20minor%20addition%20under%20your%20sheets.%20I%20never%20had%20problems%20with%20it%20shifting%20around%20or%20becoming%20loose.%20I%20felt%20its%20padding%20slightly%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20change%20the%20feel%20of%20my%20existing%20mattress.%20More%20importantly%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20the%20internal%20tubes%20that%20heat%20and%20cool%20the%20cover.%20You%20will%20feel%20the%20water%20moving%20through%20from%20time%20to%20time%20but%20mostly%20when%20it's%20cooling%20off.%20The%20water%20movement%20also%20isn't%20as%20sharp%20or%20stark%20on%20this%20new%20model%20as%20it%20was%20on%20former%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290e696bb-5f98-4bb5-b1f5-71f79a175e3d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comparing%20the%20Pod%203%20and%20Pod%204%20options%5C%22%3EComparing%20the%20Pod%203%20and%20Pod%204%20options%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Pod%202%20and%20Pod%204%20sitting%20next%20to%20each%20other%20on%20a%20carpeted%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68016bbf3fe8d39283636bc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pod%204%20hub%20is%20larger%2C%20but%20quieter%20than%20its%20previous%20generations.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pod%204%20is%20the%20focus%20here%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20cheaper%20Eight%20Sleep%20Pod%20for%20sale.%20The%20Pod%203%20starts%20at%20%242%2C295%20for%20the%20queen%20size.%20A%20savings%20of%20about%20%24350%20is%20nothing%20to%20dismiss%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20feature%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20models%20are%20significant%20for%20that%20relatively%20small%20price%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20until%20recently%2C%20I%20had%20been%20using%20the%20older%20Eight%20Sleep%20Pod%202%20(Pod%20Pro)%2C%20an%20experience%20not%20too%20unlike%20the%20Pod%203.%20Comparing%20the%20two%20helped%20me%20instantly%20notice%20the%20small%2C%20but%20meaningful%20improvements%20that%20have%20come%20to%20the%20Pod%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Pod%204%20has%20a%20much%20quieter%20operation%2C%20both%20with%20the%20hub%20and%20while%20flooding%20water%20into%20the%20mattress%20cover.%20Previously%2C%20I%20could%20hear%20the%20hub%20rev%20up%20and%20blow%20air%20around%20with%20its%20internal%20fans%20as%20it%20got%20ready%20for%20bedtime.%20There%20were%20times%20that%20the%20older%20Pod%20would%20create%20loud%2C%20vibrating%20sounds%20during%20the%20night%20when%20it%20was%20moving%20water%20around.%20It%20was%20noticeable%20enough%20to%20wake%20me%20up%20a%20few%20times.%20The%20Pod%204%20had%20none%20of%20that.%20When%20I%20tested%20the%20depths%20of%20its%20cooling%20by%20turning%20it%20to%20-10%20the%20hub%20made%20a%20soft%20hum%2C%20but%20it%20was%20steady%20and%20ambient%2C%20almost%20pleasant.%20In%20general%2C%20the%20Pod%204%20hardware%20stays%20out%20of%20the%20way%20and%20nearly%20invisible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aed3e26e-6ebc-4341-9049-dd6cd6eae7bd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20it%20works%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20Eight%20Sleep%20Pod%204%20cover.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68016aaaa466d2b74ab38444%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuring%20cold%20winters%20and%20hot%20summers%2C%20I%20loved%20being%20able%20to%20adjust%20the%20temperature%20of%20my%20bed.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20tech-based%20products%2C%20the%20Eight%20Sleep%20Pod%204%20setup%20process%20runs%20through%20the%20company's%20mobile%20app.%20The%20app%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20product's%20use%20so%20it's%20best%20to%20get%20acquainted%20with%20it%20right%20from%20the%20start.%20Animated%20screens%20guide%20you%20through%20everything%20from%20applying%20the%20mattress%20cover%20and%20filling%20the%20tank%20with%20water%20to%20setting%20a%20sleep%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20set%20up%20a%20Pod%20in%20the%20past%2C%20I%20still%20appreciated%20the%20guided%20tutorial.%20It%20took%20all%20the%20guesswork%20out.%20One%20item%20to%20note%3A%20you'll%20want%20to%20start%20the%20setup%20process%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20you%20plan%20on%20going%20to%20sleep.%20The%20first%20priming%20of%20the%20cover%20can%20take%20up%20to%20two%20hours%20and%20won't%20be%20heating%20or%20cooling%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20prepared%20you%20might%20be%20for%20an%20active-temperature-controlled%20bed%2C%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20nights%20are%20a%20little%20surreal.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20things%20the%20app%20wants%20you%20to%20do%20is%20set%20a%20target%20bedtime%20so%20the%20bed%20is%20ready%20when%20you%20are.%20It's%20hard%20not%20to%20crack%20a%20smile%20when%20climbing%20into%20bed%20on%20a%20chilly%20night%20and%20having%20the%20bed%20warm%20and%20cozy%20without%20needing%20to%20think%20about%20it%20beforehand.%20Similarly%2C%20cool%20sheets%20on%20a%20hot%20summer%20night%20are%20incredibly%20relaxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20baseline%20temperature%20is%20ready%20for%20bed%2C%20with%20the%20time%20you've%20set%2C%20adjusting%20it%20hotter%20or%20cooler%20only%20takes%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%20to%20fully%20feel%20it.%20For%20reference%2C%20turning%20the%20bed%20on%20during%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20day%20and%20going%20from%200%20to%20-10%20took%20just%20under%2015%20minutes%20in%20my%20tests.%20However%2C%20that%20temperature%20was%20way%20too%20cold%20for%20me%20to%20ever%20use.%20Except%20in%20the%20most%20extreme%20cases%2C%20you%20should%20be%20able%20to%20acheive%20a%20very%20comfortable%20feeling%20in%20well%20under%2010%20minutes%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20season%20or%20time%20of%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249301bcc-d973-443f-8607-c8dbaba15009%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Automatically%20adjusts%20throughout%20the%20night%20to%20maximize%20comfort%5C%22%3EAutomatically%20adjusts%20throughout%20the%20night%20to%20maximize%20comfort%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20temperatures%20are%20hidden%20in%20the%20app%20but%20the%20Pod%204%20is%20capable%20of%20swinging%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.eightsleep.com%2Fen_us%2Fhow-cool-or-warm-does-the-pod-get-SJG6J0bS4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Pod%2520can%2520adjust%2520the%2Cwide%2520range%2520of%2520comfort%2520options.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E55%20and%20110%20degrees%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%20of%20displaying%20the%20actual%20degrees%2C%20the%20app%20starts%20with%20a%200%20baseline%20each%20night%20and%20allows%20you%20to%20move%20that%20number%20up%20and%20down%20in%20increments%20of%201%20%E2%80%94%20going%20into%20the%20negatives%20for%20cool%20and%20positives%20for%20warm.%20The%20hub%20will%20adjust%20the%20baseline%20temperature%2C%20whatever%20it%20may%20be%2C%20if%20it%20detects%20changes%20in%20your%20room's%20ambient%20temperature.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20have%20a%20bedtime%20set%20in%20the%20app%2C%20all%20changes%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20go%20each%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20you%20can%20adjust%20the%20temperature%20and%20settings%20manually%2C%20the%20secret%20sauce%20that%20Eight%20Sleep%20is%20hoping%20you%20pay%20for%20is%20its%20Autopilot%20subscription%20feature.%20The%20Pod%204%20uses%20biometric%20sensors%20to%20react%20to%20your%20body's%20movements%20as%20well%20as%20external%20sensors%20to%20monitor%20the%20room's%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20level.%20The%20goal%20of%20the%20extensive%20monitoring%20is%20for%20the%20product%20to%20automatically%20create%20a%20more%20restful%20sleep%20experience%20in%20real%20time%2C%20without%20any%20intervention%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20ago%2C%20during%20the%20product's%20initial%20rollout%2C%20I%20found%20it%20to%20provide%20mixed%20results.%20Its%20job%20is%20to%20be%20invisible%2C%20adjusting%20the%20temperature%20for%20you%20throughout%20the%20night.%20But%20early%20on%2C%20I%20woke%20up%20cold%20and%20wanted%20to%20turn%20it%20warmer.%20I%20found%20its%20results%20to%20be%20hit%20or%20miss%20for%20the%20first%20year.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20turned%20the%20Autopilot%20feature%20off%20on%20the%20old%20Pod%20Pro.%20With%20this%20new%20model%2C%20however%2C%20I've%20found%20the%20feature%20to%20be%20more%20accurate%20and%20better%20about%20guessing%20how%20to%20keep%20my%20body%20from%20waking%20up%20as%20much.%20There%20is%20more%20processing%20power%20in%20the%20Pod%204%20which%20can%20explain%20some%20of%20the%20dramatic%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20comparison%2C%20I%20tried%20manually%20controlling%20the%20new%20Pod%204%20for%20a%20night%20and%20instantly%20missed%20Autopilot.%20I%20woke%20up%20too%20hot%20twice.%20Turning%20the%20feature%20back%20on%20the%20next%20night%2C%20I%20was%20much%20more%20comfortable.%20There's%20a%20nuance%20that's%20easy%20to%20overlook%20with%20Autopilot%2C%20but%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20it%20does%20pull%20its%20weight.%20There's%20a%20Autopilot%20section%20in%20the%20app%20that%20will%20show%20how%20many%20adjustments%20it%20made%20for%20you%20during%20the%20night%20to%20help%20prove%20it's%20working%20while%20you're%20sleeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%2C%20however%2C%20has%20loved%20the%20Autopilot%20feature%20from%20its%20inception%20and%20insists%20it%20helped%20reduce%20her%20night%20sweats%20and%20better%20regulate%20her%20body's%20temperature.%20The%20new%20Pod%204%20has%20continued%20to%20live%20in%20her%20good%20graces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223557d718-bc9e-4e36-ac00-91654d604f77%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Phone-free%20controls%20for%20manual%20changes%5C%22%3EPhone-free%20controls%20for%20manual%20changes%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22phone%20free%20adjustment%20on%20side%20of%20cover%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680175563fe8d39283636d38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20can%20make%20the%20bed%20cooler%20or%20warmer%20without%20reaching%20for%20my%20phone%20by%20lightly%20tapping%20the%20side%20of%20the%20mattress%20cover.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20well%20Autopilot%20adapts%20to%20your%20body%20temperature%2C%20there%20will%20probably%20be%20times%20you%20want%20something%20different.%20The%20Pod%204%20addresses%20this%20with%20side%20controls%20that%20react%20to%20taps.%20This%20feature%20is%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%2C%20because%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20it's%20really%20disruptive%20to%20need%20to%20reach%20for%20your%20phone%2C%20while%20half%20asleep%20to%20find%20the%20app%20and%20change%20the%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20new%20tap%20area%2C%20you%20can%20roll%20over%20and%20pat%20the%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20%E2%80%94%20twice%20for%20cooling%20and%20three%20times%20for%20warming.%20I%20used%20the%20feature%20several%20times%20and%20was%20generally%20pleased%20with%20how%20well%20it%20worked.%20I%20never%20even%20needed%20to%20open%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerforming%20two%20taps%20is%20really%20easy.%20It%20worked%20every%20time%20I%20tried%20it.%20The%20bed%20gives%20two%20quick%20vibrations%20to%20confirm%20it%20recognized%20the%20interaction.%20I%20was%20skeptical%20about%20performing%20three%20taps%20but%20it%20worked.%20However%2C%20I%20did%20have%20some%20false%20positives%20with%20that%20gesture.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20juggle%20getting%20the%20bed%20to%20recognize%20three%20taps%2C%20while%20also%20not%20waking%20up%20my%20wife%20from%20smacking%20the%20bed%20too%20hard.%20The%20feature%20could%20probably%20use%20some%20refinement%20over%20time%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20good%20start%20and%20nice%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252eb0acb-05be-4206-89a4-2a3cc59a34b6%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comprehensive%20and%20accurate%20sleep%20data%5C%22%3EComprehensive%20and%20accurate%20sleep%20data%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eight%20Sleep%20app%20screenshots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68017556a466d2b74ab385f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWithin%20the%20app%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20managing%20temperature%20you%20can%20see%20detailed%20sleep%20analytics%20as%20well%20as%20information%20about%20how%20the%20Pod%204%20adjusted%20to%20your%20needs%20overnight%20to%20help%20improve%20sleep.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20half%20of%20the%20Autopilot%20subscription%2C%20along%20with%20real-time%20temperature%20adjustments%2C%20is%20its%20dual-zone%20sleep%20tracking.%20It%20will%20keep%20track%20of%20vitals%20like%20heart%20rate%2C%20respiratory%20rate%2C%20resting%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20heart%20rate%20variability.%20It%20also%20documents%20the%20time%20you%20get%20into%20and%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20to%20fall%20asleep%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20deep%20and%20light%20sleep.%20This%20is%20a%20way%20to%20capture%20sleep%20data%20without%20needing%20to%20wear%20a%20watch%20or%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extensive%20results%20are%20displayed%20in%20the%20app%20and%20can%20be%20simultaneously%20funneled%20into%20Apple%20Health.%20How%20accurate%20is%20the%20data%3F%20I%20have%20several%20years%20of%20this%20data%20in%20the%20Eight%20Sleep%20app%20and%20it%20all%20lines%20up%20with%20what%20I've%20seen%20and%20felt.%20For%20example%2C%20I've%20verified%20that%20it%20does%20a%20phenomenal%20job%20of%20knowing%20when%20I%20get%20in%20bed%20at%20night%20to%20watch%20a%20show%20and%20when%20I%20actually%20fall%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Pod%204%2C%20I%20directly%20compared%20its%20sleep%20tracking%20with%20my%20Oura%20ring%20sleep%20data.%20The%20metrics%20vary%20because%20the%20devices%20are%20measuring%20from%20different%20points%20of%20contact%2C%20but%20the%20data%20from%20both%20was%20consistent.%20The%20results%20mirrored%20each%20other%20pretty%20well%20and%20matched%20how%20I%20felt%20after%20each%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20subscription%20also%20includes%20the%20vibration%20and%20thermal%20alarm%20to%20wake%20you%20up%20within%20a%20time%20frame%20that%20makes%20sense%20for%20your%20sleep%20cycle.%20I%20haven't%20tried%20the%20adjustable%20base%20portion%20of%20the%20Pod%204%20Ultra%2C%20but%20if%20you%20go%20that%20route%2C%20Autopilot%20can%20detect%20snoring%20and%20move%20the%20base%20on%20its%20own%20to%20mitigate%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutopilot%20is%20required%20for%20at%20least%20one%20year%20so%20you're%20looking%20at%20a%20minimum%20of%20%24200%20for%20the%20service%20(or%20%24250%20for%20the%20one%20with%20the%20five-year%20warranty).%20That's%20a%20sneaky%20way%20of%20getting%20people%20to%20try%20and%20potentially%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20an%20expensive%20service.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20pull%20the%20trigger%20on%20Autopilot%20blindly%20at%20checkout%2C%20if%20it%20weren't%20required%2C%20but%20after%20having%20tried%20it%2C%20I%20would%20also%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20cancel%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228745d2bb-e6c1-45a7-8f94-1d5d27c398ad%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3EPrice%20is%20a%20big%20consideration%2C%20but%20not%20as%20much%20as%20you%20might%20think%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C