nicipal%20Corporation%20(BMC).%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20watched%20it%20%5Bthe%20walkway%5D%20come%20up%20little%20by%20little.%20Seeing%20it%20in%20its%20present%20form%20is%20a%20dream%20come%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20explains.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99re%20shaded%20by%20a%20canvas%20of%20green%20that%20dances%20above%20our%20heads.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380299%2Fnovember-march-best-time-visit-vedanthangal-bird-sanctuary-migration-season-birdwatching%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20forest%20is%20an%20archive%20of%20%3Cem%3Egulmohar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20copperpod%2C%20mango%2C%20coconut%2C%20rain%20tree%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejamun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20jackfruit%20trees.%20Our%20company%20is%20audio-visual%3B%20while%20the%20trees%20make%20for%20a%20pretty%20sight%2C%20the%20chirp%20of%20birds%20cracks%20into%20the%20silent%20interludes%20during%20our%20walk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FoGe7fJ31WtY%3Fsi%3DBSt-lXl_TiBY7W6N%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%E2%80%99s%20design%20mastery%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20He%20is%20following%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20a%20fabled%20architectural%20legacy.%20His%20father%2C%20Iftikhar%20Kadri%20%E2%80%94%20now%2097%20%E2%80%94%20gave%20Mumbai%20its%20beloved%20Nehru%20Centre%2C%20a%20living%20memorial%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Iftikhar%20had%20mentioned%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20the%20design%20was%20born%20out%20of%20wanting%20it%20to%20reflect%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20ideals%2C%20with%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20cylindrical%20shape%20portraying%20a%20nation%20reaching%20up%20towards%20the%20sky%20and%20its%20cross%20latticework%20alluding%20to%20the%20whorls%20of%20the%20rose%20flower%20that%20Nehru%20always%20wore%20in%20his%20lapel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20his%20father%2C%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20genius%20lies%20in%20architecting%20places%20that%20are%20rich%20with%20possibilities.%20His%20architectural%20vocabulary%20is%20angled%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386103%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-green-pavers-cseb-earth-blocks-orient-stranded-board%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimplistic%20design%20that%20aces%20functionality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20reasons%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20design%20needed%20to%20be%20simple%3B%20I%20wanted%20people%20to%20experience%20the%20forest%20and%20its%20views.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20the%20structure%20to%20be%20too%20intrusive%20within%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%20I%20agree%2C%20the%20walkway%20cuts%20through%20the%20forest%20with%20finesse%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20way%20of%20hope%20through%20the%20urban%20sprawl%20that%20skirts%20around%20its%20perimeter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20trees%20were%20cut%20for%20the%20project.%E2%80%9D%20The%20walkway%20has%20found%20its%20safe%20space%2C%20its%20Merbau%20wood%20torso%20supported%20by%20epoxy-coated%20steel%20columns%2C%20cradled%20by%20the%20land%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20huge%20hammock%20that%20fin