r%20playfields%2C%20we%20could%20actually%20walk%20into%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20forest%2C%20you%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20Rahul%20playing.%20Instead%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20see%20him%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F415182%2Ftrekking-with-kids-beginner-friendly-trails-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20the%20wilderness%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Around%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20the%20Malabar%20area%20in%20Mumbai%20shared%20ground%20with%20hyenas%20and%20jackals.%C2%A0With%20time%2C%20buildings%20and%20skyscrapers%20dotted%20its%20skyline%2C%20and%20what%20remained%20of%20the%20jungle%20was%20a%2012-acre%20microbiome%20where%20rose-ringed%20parakeet%2C%20coppersmith%20barbet%2C%20and%20golden%20oriole%20continue%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20walks%20along%20the%20nature%20trail%2C%20a%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu%20creeps%20up%20on%20him.%20He%20recalls%20venturing%20into%20the%20Malabar%20Forest%20when%20he%20was%20around%2011%20years%20old%20with%20his%20dog%2C%20walking%2C%20exploring%2C%20and%20wondering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20afraid%20of%20being%20in%20the%20forest%20by%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20known%20to%20find%20pathways%2C%20to%20intuitively%20know%20the%20way.%E2%80%9D%20He%20did%20not%20need%20a%20GPS%2C%20he%20was%20guided%20by%20the%20rhythms%20of%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20design%20philosophy%20backed%20by%20sustainable%20sensibilities%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesign%20viability%20and%20beautiful%20views%20convene%20in%20the%20nature%20trail%3B%20its%20Sea%20Viewing%20Deck%20offering%20the%20average%20visitor%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20their%20city%20through%20a%20new%20lens.%20Through%20the%20482%20metres%20it%20covers%2C%20the%20walkway%20embodies%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20vision%